<div id="review_781116299" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/781116299" />
    <a title="Thandiwe Nxumalo" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/26261157-thandiwe-nxumalo"><img alt="Thandiwe Nxumalo" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1386186488p2/26261157.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/781116299?book_show_action=true">Dec 04, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Thandiwe Nxumalo" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Thandiwe Nxumalo" href="/user/show/26261157-thandiwe-nxumalo">Thandiwe Nxumalo</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer781116299" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2426258157047273473">The Sabi is a much needed book in South Africa. it is more than an autobiography it is moment in time in South Africa and it speaks to everyone across the board. The author has a conversation with the reader and takes him or her on a journey with her into her mind, into her circumstances and into the history of South Africa. More than anything sit back, read the book and enjoy it!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


